Client's birthday is not tracked.

Tracking client's birthday will allow automated greeting when it is
client's birthday.

Let's
* Add date utility class for common use.
* Add birthday to model.
* Enable storage to handle birthday.
* Add client command and edit client command should handle birthdays.
* Update UI to show birthday.
* Update all data for testing and sample data.
* Update all test cases for existing files and update for new classes.

* Update all test cases for existing files and update for new classes.

commitResults.messageBody:
Birthday has been implemented, but reminders for birthday still to be
added to make meaningful use of birthday.

Birthday reminders will enable users to be reminded of birthdays from
now to the following week.

Let's
* Add birthday reminders panel in ui.
* Add a method to obtain the list of persons in the birthday reminders
list to LogicManager, ModelManager, AddressBook and UniquePersonList.
* Add method to identify person with upcoming birthday in Person
and Birthday.

commitResults.messageBody:
Bug detected with sorting when other commands happen, such as sorting
then adding policy. Bug detected with not updating client view after
sorting.

Refactoring sorting will allow filteredPersons to revert to being
immutable and final, while allowing combinations of both
sorting and filtering effects.

Let's
* Refactor sort, by storing the comparator in model and allowing this
to be set.
* Layer of sorting logic when filtered list is obtained, so that
filtered list can remain immutable.
* Abstract setting the display of client to the first person in the
sorted and filtered list, since its used in find, sort and list

commitResults.messageBody:
Let's
* Birthday reminders now sort by month and day only and regardless of
year.
* Separate comparator method for sorting by month and day only for
birthday reminders, since we still need to reserve the comparator that
sorts by year, month and date for the sort client list by birthday
function.
* Use withYear() when disregarding date, so that 29 Feb is truncated to
28 Feb on non-leap years.
